com.android.build.api.attributes

Interface BuildTypeAttr

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Named

    public interface BuildTypeAttr
extends Named
    Type for the attribute holding BuildType information.

    There should only be one build type attribute associated to each Configuration object. The key should be ATTRIBUTE.
